bindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104qld1665702770378.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qld1665702770378.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qld1665702770378.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"qld1665702770378\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"qld1665702770378__unifacecomponent_421417\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Base class from which individual Uniface component classes are derived.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"qld1665702770378__topic_d128696e1_d128697e1_d128698e1\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104qld1665702770378_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"qld1665702770378__codeblock_ukj_x5v_cwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">import com.rocketsoftware.uniface.jci*;public class MyComponentName extends UnifaceComponent;\nMyComponentName(Properties instProp)</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qld1665702770378__topic_d91167e1_d91168e1_d91169e1_d91170e1_d91171e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1226833e58\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qld1665702770378__p_d128702e1_d128703e1_d128704e1\"><span class=\"keyword apiname\">UnifaceComponent</span> is the base\n            class of the Java call-in. It provides the classes that implement the\n               <span class=\"keyword apiname\">activate</span> method. <span class=\"keyword apiname\">UnifaceComponent</span> calls\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">newinstance</span> when it is instantiated.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qld1665702770378__topic_d91172e1_d91173e1_d91174e1_d91175e1_d91176e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1226833e78\">Constructor</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qld1665702770378__p_d128708e1_d128709e1_d128710e1\">The following constructor produces a Java file:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104qld1665702770378_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"qld1665702770378__codeblock_cyg_dvv_cwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">ComponentName ( Properties instProp)</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qld1665702770378__li_d46445e1_d46446e1_d46447e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ComponentName</var> is the Java equivalent of the Uniface component’s\n               name. For example, MY_MATH becomes <code class=\"ph codeph\">MyMath</code>. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qld1665702770378__li_d46448e1_d46449e1_d46450e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">instProp</code>—instance properties. The property supported is the Uniface component ID. This property is usually filled by the generated Java file, and is used to compare the version of the generated Java file with the signature in the UAR.\n </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qld1665702770378__p_d128714e1_d128715e1_d128716e1\">If you want to disable component ID checking\n            (useful during component development), specify an empty string as component ID. For\n            example, if the component name is MY_MATH, the class name will be\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">MyMath</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104qld1665702770378_html_2\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"qld1665702770378__codeblock_ugh_gvv_cwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">// Disable component ID checking for MyMath.\nProperties instProps = new Properties();\ninstProps.put (\"component_id\", \"\");\nMyMath m = new MyMath(instProps);</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qld1665702770378__p_d128717e1_d128718e1_d128719e1\">The following constructor produces a JavaBean file:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" id=\"qld1665702770378__codeblock_akt_hvv_cwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">ComponentName Bean ()</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qld1665702770378__topic_d91177e1_d91178e1_d91179e1_d91180e1_d91181e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1226833e124\">Methods</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qld1665702770378__p_d128726e1_d128727e1_d128728e1\">The following Java methods correspond to Uniface triggers and operations:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qld1665702770378__li_d46451e1_d46452e1_d46453e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"pmi1665702770448.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pmi1665702770448.html\" title=\"This method activates the requested operation.\">UnifaceComponent.activate</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qld1665702770378__li_d46454e1_d46455e1_d46456e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hkh1665702770516.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hkh1665702770516.html\" title=\"This method calls the accept trigger.\">UnifaceComponent.accept</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qld1665702770378__li_d46457e1_d46458e1_d46459e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rup1665702770584.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rup1665702770584.html\" title=\"This method call the exec operation.\">UnifaceComponent.exec</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qld1665702770378__li_d46460e1_d46461e1_d46462e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bgj1665702770660.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bgj1665702770660.html\" title=\"The method remove deletes the component instance.\">UnifaceComponent.remove</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qld1665702770378__li_d46463e1_d46464e1_d46465e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hun1665702770733.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hun1665702770733.html\" title=\"This method calls the quit trigger.\">UnifaceComponent.quit</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531313\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531313\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "UnifaceComponent Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Base class from which individual Uniface component classes are derived. Explain this code import com.rocketsoftware.uniface.jci*;public class MyComponentName extends UnifaceComponent; MyComponentName(Properties instProp) Copy Description UnifaceComponent is the base class of the Java call-in. It provides the classes that implement the activate method. UnifaceComponent calls newinstance when it is instantiated. Constructor The following constructor produces a Java file: Explain this code ComponentName ( Properties instProp) Copy ComponentName is the Java equivalent of the Uniface component’s name. For example, MY_MATH becomes MyMath . instProp —instance properties. The property supported is the Uniface component ID. This property is usually filled by the generated Java file, and is used to compare the version of the generated Java file with the signature in the UAR. If you want to disable component ID checking (useful during component development), specify an empty string as component ID. For example, if the component name is MY_MATH, the class name will be MyMath : Explain this code // Disable component ID checking for MyMath. Properties instProps = new Properties(); instProps.put (\"component_id\", \"\"); MyMath m = new MyMath(instProps); Copy The following constructor produces a JavaBean file: ComponentName Bean () Copy Methods The following Java methods correspond to Uniface triggers and operations: UnifaceComponent.activate UnifaceComponent.accept UnifaceComponent.exec UnifaceComponent.remove UnifaceComponent.quit Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}